Open‑Core Scope

This MIT license applies only to the open‑source modules published under the
@silence scope that form the open‑core framework:

- @silence/contracts
- @silence/events
- @silence/behavioral-sequences
- @silence/rhythmic-patterns
- @silence/cognitive-load
- @silence/capacity-recovery
- @silence/attention-profiles
- @silence/language
- @silence/validator
- @silence/ui

These packages may be used independently in external projects under the terms
of the MIT license.

Closed and Enterprise Modules

All closed modules published under the @silence/ee scope, as well as any
